```{r pancreas 32060129, include=FALSE}

PMID_32060129 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32060129', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32060129 <- paste0(PMID_32060129$journal,' ', PMID_32060129$year, ' ', PMID_32060129$month,';', PMID_32060129$volume,'(', PMID_32060129$number,'):', PMID_32060129$pages)

PubMed_32060129 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32060129$eprint)

doi_32060129 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32060129$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
